{
  "id": "adv_bond_rio_01_04",
  "title": "神崎莉央4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "葵、夕食出来たわよ\nゲームは中断して、食べましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ dinner is ready\nStop your game and let's eat",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gun-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4600.000000000001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gun-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5790.7082796
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gun-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7633.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待ってて。このゾンビ、なかなか倒せないんだ\nさすがにボスキャラは手強いな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on a second. This zombie is really tough to beat\nAs expected of a boss character‚ it's putting up a fight",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "食事の前に、そんな怖いゲームはやめてちょうだい\nほら、冷めないうちに食べるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please stop playing such a scary game before a meal\nCome on‚ eat it before it gets cold",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gun-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6666.666666599997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "よし、倒した。一時中断っと……\nあ、今日はカレーなんだね。いただきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ got him. Pausing for now…\nOh‚ it's curry today. Thanks for the food",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4011.9719751
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、美味しい。莉央はやっぱり料理が上手だね\n実家が飲食店なだけはあるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm‚ delicious. You really are a great cook‚ Rio\nIt shows that you grew up in a restaurant family",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "何度も言うけど、飲食店と言っても小さな喫茶店よ\nカレーもメニューにあったから、慣れてるだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've told you many times‚ it's just a small café\nI'm just used to making curry because it was on the menu",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "特別なスパイスも具材も使われてないけど\nホッとする味だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn't use any special spices or ingredients‚\nbut it's a very comforting taste",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そう？　私は葵の作るカレーも好きよ\n次は貴方が作ってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? I like the curry you make too‚ Aoi\nYou should make it next time",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、僕の素人料理より莉央の方が美味しいよ\n東京で支店を開いたら、大繁盛間違いなしだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ yours is much better than my amateur cooking\nIf you opened a branch in Tokyo‚ it would definitely be a huge hit",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ貴方、私をおだてて自分の料理当番を\nサボる気でしょ。ダメよ、ちゃんとやりなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ you're just praising me to slack off\non your turn to cook‚ aren't you? No way‚ do your job properly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "莉央はツレないな。半分は本気なのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're so cold‚ Rio. Half of that was actually sincere",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、僕はそんな風にしっかりしてる莉央も好きだよ\nお嫁さんにもらいたいくらいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I like that you're so level-headed too\nI'd almost want to take you as my wife",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "あのねえ、貴方はお嫁さんをもらうんじゃなくて\nなる方でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good grief‚ you're not the one taking a wife‚\nyou're the one becoming one‚ aren't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、こないだ愛とこころと四人で話している時も\nそんなこと言ってたわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ right. You said the same thing when we were\ntalking with Ai and Kokoro the other day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1999959309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったね。……あ、そういえば二人きりで\nご飯を食べるの、なんだか久しぶりな気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true. …Oh‚ come to think of it‚\nit feels like it's been a while since it was just the two of us eating",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.3666625976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "昔はいつも二人きりだったわね……\nたまにはいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We used to always be alone together back then…\nWouldn't it be okay sometimes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0666625976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "うん、なんだかホッとする。君は僕にとって特別だから\nこれからもよろしく、莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I feel at ease. Because you're special to me\nI'm looking forward to our time together‚ Rio",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4666625976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_04-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "真顔でそういうこと言わない！\n……でも、私こそよろしく、葵",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't say things like that with such a straight face!\n…But‚ likewise‚ Aoi",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7333292643,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}